Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(725,655)}norn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才刚醒就放没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查探对方的想法还是能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也控制不了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伦 展开完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3、第4重力波防护罩展开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战场形成完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜部队 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伦 开始与乌西亚型交战
