Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体留在原地 可别轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 系统是剑司前辈在操纵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的统帅就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都要活着回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不能死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的想法 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诺伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我们承担了绪战的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁在操纵这些遥控机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还是担心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人正在学习岛的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕程序 启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来比剑术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都行吗…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这群东西是抢夺武器用的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,针对各部机体的特性派出的个体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 天照 位置变更
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 只要打倒一只
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的就都不成问题了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你退下了吧！
