Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预测了我的动作！
