Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员无法脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CDC 暂时解除防护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 史彦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是保护龙宫岛的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要还有力量 就不能退出战场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还有力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛…要保护龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保护乙姬的岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 严重损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员生死未卜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齐格飞系统 无响应！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把你干掉…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3重力波防护罩 正被敌人的攻击削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天照 坠落！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein和Mk.Nicht呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还处于第三启动阶段
