Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Ⅲ调出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了开发无人机 已经把整个系统重制了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系！我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 重新启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…为什么 还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…怎么像一骑前辈一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是 怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这武器是从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器库里的武器正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有射出的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各机的内核…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内核正在增殖！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜全机 继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机库报告机体内核正在发生未知现象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将我唤醒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你们而存在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安分点 亡灵们！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我控制这个怪物的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于…把怪物的封印解开了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP配乐插入)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认Mk.Nicht与Mk.Sein启动！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein…醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 留在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其余各机交换位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更换战斗对象 互相掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保护龙宫岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护乙姬的岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要守住！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP歌词插入)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机动手臂上闪耀高帕标志之时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代代相传的灵魂正是折不断的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超必杀·高帕一闪！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你漫画中毒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过反正像一骑前辈那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做就对了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的愿望只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是长久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 为此我们行使的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却总是与和平相去甚远的力量
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
